  "time_ut": 1661159492,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d86\u0db6\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dd2\u0dad \u0db4\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dbd\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0dbb\u0da2\u0dba\u0dda \u0d85\u0db1\u0dd4\u0d9c\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc4\u0dba \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dda",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Government support for disabled people will be increased",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Ajith Rajapaksa, Deputy Speaker of the Parliament, said that the government is working to increase the support provided by the government to self-employed persons with disabilities.",
        "He also mentioned that the matter of increasing the support provided by the government to such persons has already been brought to the attention of the government.",
        "The Deputy Speaker said that about 100,000 people with various disabilities are engaged in self-employment across the country and also stated that nearly 500 people with disabilities apply for self-employment opportunities in a year."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
